main event: Objects were observed over Venice, California, on September 8, 1962, appearing extremely fast and emitting light or energy.
interesting points: One observer noted a routine aircraft object that disappeared behind clouds and then reappeared brightly for a few seconds., The object was described as self-luminous with a dull reddish-orange color., A separate report described a UFO as an oval-shaped white saucer witnessed at sunset., The saucer was confirmed by family members of the observer., The Air Force expressed interest in the potential national security threat posed by unidentified aerial phenomena.
sighted object: unidentified flying objects emitting light or energy
